Bulk RNAseq

1. loading package and data

1.1. R package

library("DESeq2")
library("ComplexHeatmap")
library("magrittr")
library("RColorBrewer")
library("ggplot2")
library("ggpubr")
library("org.Mm.eg.db")
library("AnnotationDbi")
library("data.table")
library("dplyr")

1.2. DESeq2 Object

dds <- readRDS("../Data/DESeq2_Bulk_RNAseq.Rds")

1.3. GSVA Results

GSVA_res <- readRDS("../Data/GSVA_Bulk_RNAseq.Rds")

2. Sample Distance

2.1. PCA plot

rld <- rlog(dds,blind=FALSE)
pcaData <- plotPCA(rld, intgroup = c("Group"), returnData = TRUE,ntop=Inf)
percentVar <- round(100 * attr(pcaData, "percentVar"))
ggplot(pcaData, aes(x = PC1, y = PC2, color =Group)) +
  geom_point(size =5) +
  xlab(paste0("PC1: ", percentVar[1], "% variance")) +
  ylab(paste0("PC2: ", percentVar[2], "% variance")) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette="Dark2")+theme_classic2()+
  theme(legend.text = element_text(size=15),legend.title = element_text(size=18))

2.2. Plot

Mat <- counts(dds,normalized=T)
Mat%<>%t()%>%scale%>%t()
Dist <- dist(Mat%>%t(),upper = T)%>%as.matrix()
Cluster<- Mat%>%t()%>%dist()%>%hclust()
manual_order = c("BM1", "BM1", "Soft1", "Soft2","Stiff1","Stiff2","TCPS1", "TCPS2")
dend  <-  reorder(as.dendrogram(Cluster), wts=order(match(manual_order, rownames(Dist))))
col_cluster <- as.hclust(dend)
ComplexHeatmap::Heatmap(Dist,col = colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 11, name ="RdYlBu")))(100),
                        show_column_names = F
                        ,cluster_columns = col_cluster,cluster_rows = col_cluster
                        ,name = "Distance"
                        )

3. Pathway showing

3.1. Preparing Data

Dist <- dist(GSVA_res%>%t(),upper = T)%>%as.matrix()
Cluster<- GSVA_res%>%t()%>%dist()%>%hclust(method = "ward.D2")
manual_order = c("BM1", "BM1", "Soft1", "Soft2","Stiff1","Stiff2","TCPS1", "TCPS2")
dend  <-  reorder(as.dendrogram(Cluster), wts=order(match(manual_order, rownames(Dist))))
col_cluster <- as.hclust(dend)

3.2. Plot

P1 <- Heatmap(GSVA_res,
              show_row_names = T,
              show_column_names = F,
              cluster_columns = F,
              cluster_rows =  F,
              column_names_side = "top",
              col=colorRampPalette(rev(brewer.pal(n = 7, name ="RdBu")))(100),
              name = "Expression",width=unit(6,"cm"),
              heatmap_legend_param = list(direction = "horizontal",legend_width =unit(4,"cm"),legend_height=unit(10,"cm")),
              column_split = c(1,1,2,2,3,3,4,4),column_title = c("BM","Soft","Stiff","TCPS"),
              row_split = rep(c(1,2,3),c(4,1,10)),row_title = c("","",""),
              border = T,border_gp = gpar(col = 'black', lwd = 2)
              )

draw(P1, heatmap_legend_side = "bottom")

4. Gene show

4.1. Mapping gene names

Expr <- counts(dds,normalized=T)
#
Data <- data.table(
  ENSEMBEL = rownames(Expr)
)
Data$SYMBOL<-mapIds(org.Mm.eg.db,keys=Data$ENSEMBEL,column="SYMBOL",keytype="ENSEMBL",multiVals="first")
## 'select()' returned 1:many mapping between keys and columns
Data <- subset(Data,!is.na(Data$SYMBOL))
Expr <- Expr[Data$ENSEMBEL,]
rownames(Expr) <- Data$SYMBOL

4.2. Plot

Gene <- c("Kit","Flt3","Ly6c1","Ly6c2",
          "Cd68","Piezo1","Lmna","Rhoa"
          )

#
Plot_data <- Expr[Gene,]%>%as.data.frame()
Plot_data$Genename <- rownames(Plot_data)
Plot_data%<>%as.data.table()
Plot_data%<>%melt()
## Warning in melt.data.table(.): id.vars and measure.vars are internally guessed
## when both are 'NULL'. All non-numeric/integer/logical type columns are
## considered id.vars, which in this case are columns [Genename, ...]. Consider
## providing at least one of 'id' or 'measure' vars in future.
colnames(Plot_data) <- c("Genename","Sample","Expression")
Plot_data$Group <- gsub("[1-9]","",Plot_data$Sample)
Plot_data%<>%as.data.table()
#
setorder(Plot_data,Genename)


PlotGenelist <- lapply(Gene,function(x){
data <- Plot_data[Genename==x]
data_summary <- data %>%
  group_by(Group) %>%
  summarise(
    mean = mean(Expression),
    se = sd(Expression) / sqrt(n())
  )
ggplot(data_summary, aes(x = Group, y = mean)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge", aes(fill = Group)) +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = mean - se, ymax = mean + se), width = 0.2) +
  theme_bw() +ggsci::scale_fill_jama()+
  labs(x = "Group",y = "Mean Value")+ggtitle(x)+
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 10),axis.text = element_text(size = 10),plot.title = element_text(size = 10,hjust = .5),legend.position = "none")
}
)

cowplot::plot_grid(plotlist = PlotGenelist,ncol = 4)
